oloji) Dernegi&#x27;nin Yayin organidir = The journal of the Turkish Society of Algology</i> 27(1) 1–11. DOI:<a href=\"https://doi.org/10.5505/agri.2015.79663\">10.5505/agri.2015.79663</a>  PUBMED:<a href=\"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/25867868/\">https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/25867868</a></p></li></ol></body></html>",
